creator: TikiP Studio
descriptionHtml:
Fake Video calling is so funny and trendy. You can video call your friends, family, and colleagues, sharing your face and surroundings simultaneously. Being in the same location all time is boring, right? How about appearing with your regular face? Everyone knows what that looks like.

What if you could make a fake video call that switched out your face, the background, or other important features—would you fake call your family?

Here's how fake video calls work and how you can spot one.

You can create a fake call or fake video applications with this app. Users can create fake calls with videos like celebrity videos included in the application. They choose a countdown timer for a fake call, fake call occurs when the countdown is over. When the user answers the call, the pre-selected video like a celebrity video is displayed. It also shows the user on the front camera. In short, it works just like a video call!

For instance, you could create a fake video background in an attempt to trick people into believing you're on holiday. You could record a video of yourself staring at your monitor, then play it back during a meeting that you are not required to talk in.

Download Fake Video Call, Prank Dial App to prank our friends and have fun :))
